info.author: Grok project
info.name: martian
info.summary: Martian is a library that allows the embedding of configuration information in Python code. Martian can then grok the system and do the appropriate configuration registrations. One example of a system that uses Martian is the system where it originated: Grok (http://grok.zope.org)
